== Who I Am ==
My name is Jesse Sung and is a member of Ubuntu kernel team since August 2011. I've worked on several derivative kernels including kernels for Intel IoTG, Mediatek, Xilinx, and some project ones.

== My Ubuntu Story ==
I'm a long time Debian user since mid-1990 and was interested to try out something new (but similar) at some point around 2010. That was when I started to use Ubuntu and keep it as my daily driver since then.

== My Involvement ==
I started my journey from working on the generic kernel after joining Canonical, and then extended the adventure to quite a few derivative kernels.
